12 Geh8 6 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Sou2-i2 tioh8 sann chiap-lap8, chhin-chhiunn7 Ki-tok u7 chiap-lap8 lin2. (Lo5-ma2 15:7)
Ti7 40 ni5-cheng5, u7 chit8 e5 chheng-lian5 lang5, mia5 Ka-sin3, i si7 chit8 e5 chin lau2-sit8 e5 chheng-lian5. U7 chit8-pai2 khia5-chhia tui3 Hoa-lian5-kang2 beh kau3 Tai5-tang e5 sou2-chai7.
Hit-si5 tu2-tu2 si7 chiann-geh8 chin koann5 e5 si5-hau7, chheng-lian5 lang5 chin ai3 un7-tong7, koh hit e5 si5-chun7 hoe2-chhia, a2-si7 khi3-chhia bo5 chhin-chhiunn7 chit-chun7 chiah hoat-tat8; na7 m7-si7 khia5-chhia, chiu7-si7 kiann5-lou7. Chin kho2-sioh Ka-sin3 beh chhut-mng5 e5 si5, bo5 chim-chiok i e5 chhia u7 ho2-se3 a2-bo5, chiu7 chhut-hoat, Ka-sin3 chin khoai3-lok8, na2 khia5-chhia na2 gim5-si.
Jit8-thau5 teh loh8-soann chin kin2, tit8-tit8 am3-khi3; tann i2-keng bo5 khoann3-kinn3 lou7, ti7 hia long2 si7 soa-pou, Ka-sin3 chin tioh8-kip, koh khoann3-kinn3 si3-ui5 long2 bo5 chhu3, iu7-koh pak-tou2 ia7 teh iau, ia7 chin koann5; chiu7 chhut-lat8 tah8-chhia, bo5 phah-sng3 sou2 teh khia5 e5 chhia-lian2 soa3 phoa3-khang, bo5 hoat-tou7 thang koh chin3-heng5.
Ti7 hia teh kiann-hiann5 e5 tiong-kan, hut-jian5 ti7 soa-pou u7 khoann3-kinn3 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7 kng-kng e5 khoan2, Ka-sin3 chiu7 chiong chhia ban7-ban7 khan kau3 hit sou2-chai7, ko2-jian5 u7 chit8-keng chhu3. I chiu7 ka7 phah-mng5, lai7-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 oa2 60 hoe3 e5 lau7-lang5 lai5 khui mng5, chit8-e7 khui-khui chiu7 toa7-siann hoah kong2, Li2 si7 chhat8 beh lai5 chhiunn2 goan2 e5 mih8, goa2 bo5 mih8 thang hou7 li2, kin2-chau2, kin2-chau2, na7 m7 chau2, (hit-si5 a-peh tui3 i e5 lak8-te7-a2 giah8 chit8 ki to chhut-lai5) kong2, goa2 beh lai5 kap li2 chhi3 khoann3 le3. Hit-si5 Ka-sin3 chin kiann ka7 i kong2, Lau7 a-peh-a2, goa2 m7-si7 chhat8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 lau2-sit8 lang5, in-ui7 goa2 e5 chhia e5 chhiu7-leng khi3 hou7 phoa3-khi3, chhiann2 li2 hou7 goa2 kia3 chit-tai5 chhia, koh hou7 goa2 tiam3 chia koe3 chit8-am3, in-ui7 chin koann5 goa2 bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 chiu7 beh chhut-mng5, chhiann2 li2 tong5-cheng5 goa2 le3; goa2 sit8-chai7 m7-si7 chhat8-a2. Lau7 a-peh koh-khah toa7-siann kong2, Beh chau2 li2 tioh8 chau2, na7 m7 beh hou7 li2 si2.
Ti7 in lai7-bin7 lau7 a-m2 teh khun3 thiann-kinn3 mng5-goa7 si7 chainn2-iunn7, chiu7 khi2-lai5, tu2-tu2 hit-si5 Ka-sin3 beh li7-khui i e5 chhu3, lau7 a-m2 chhut-siann kio3, siau3-lian5 lang5 li2 ban7 chiah khi3, chiu7 mng7 khoann3 si7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3. Ka-sin3 long2 lau2-sit8 tui3 thau5 kau3-boe2 kong2 hou7 i thiann. Lau7 a-m2 chin hoann-hi2 kong2, Chhiann2 li2 jip8-lai5 koe3-lou7 lang5, goa2 tioh8-ai3 ho2-le2 chiap-thai7 li2.
Chong2-si7 lau7 a-peh ti7 pinn-a2 chin siu7-khi3, kong2, E7-am3 teh-beh tioh8 chhat8-thau lah, li2 chit8-koa2 phoa3-sann-a2-khou3 m7-kiann hou7 i thau-theh8 khi3. Ka-sin3 kong2, Lau7 a-peh goa2 to ka7 li2 kong2 liau2, goa2 m7-si7 chhat8-a2, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 sin3 Ia5-sou e5 lang5, lau7 a-peh thiann-tioh8 i si7 sin3 Ia5-sou, chiu7 chin hoann-hi2, na7-si7 sin3 Ia5-sou e5 lang5 chin ho2, goa2 u7 chit8-pai2 iu5-goan5 m7 tu2-ho2 lou7-cham7, u7 chit8 e5 sin3 Ia5-sou e5 lang5 chin ho2-le2 chiap-lap8 goa2. Tann chin sit-le2, chhiann2 li2 kin2 jip8-lai5, chiu7 kin2 chu2 chit8-koa2 sio-moe5 hou7 i chiah8, hit-am3 chhiann2 i ti7 hia koe3-mi5.
Tann sio2 peng5-iu2, Ia5-sou Ki-tok u7 chiap-lap8 lan2 cho3 i e5 peng5-iu2, na7 u7 lang5 e5 tang5-phoann7 lai5 cho3 lan2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 hak8-seng, lan2 tioh8 ho2-le2 chiap-thai7 i, m7-thang kap i oan-ke, m7-thang koann2 i, tioh8 chhin-chhiat lai5 in2-chhoa7 i, chiu7 Ia5-sou ia7 beh chiap-lap8 lan2.
(koh sann-kap lai5 liam7 kim-ku3) (Ang5 Siok-kheng)
