Kim-ku3: Tann goa2 chin-chiann3 chai Siong7-te3 bo5 eng7 goa7-mau7 chhu2 lang5. (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 10:34)
Cha2-cheng5 ti7 Tai5-lam5 hu7-kin7 e5 hiong-chhoan u7 chit8 e5 lau7-toa7 lang5, mia5 kio3 “Chong2-chek-a3”. I si7 choh-chhan5 lang5, bo5 sim2-mih8 hak8-bun7, chong2-si7 ti7 in e5 te7-hng si7 cham2-jian5 ho2-giah8 e5 lang5.
U7 chit8-pai2 i beh khi3 Tai5-lam5, eng-kai i tioh8 che7 chhia khi3, chong2-si7 i m7-kam liau2 chinn5 che7 chhia, sou2-i2 i chiu7 thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5, eng7 kiann5-lou7 beh khi3 Tai5-lam5. I siunn7 kong2, beh khi3 Hu2-siann5 (Tai5-lam5 e5 kou2-cha2 mia5) leh, na7 bo5 chheng7-e5 e7 hou7 lang5 chhio3, sou2-i2 tioh8 chheng7-e5 lai5-khi3, m7-ku2 i koh siunn7 kong2, na7 chheng7-e5, kiann5 kau3 Tai5-lam5, chiu7 e5 e7 khoai3 phainn2, sou2-i2 i chiu7 koat-teng7 thng3 khi2-lai5 eng7 theh8--e5, kau3 beh kau3-ui7 e5 si5 chiah lai5 chheng7. Chong2-chek-a3 chiu7 an2-ni thng3 chhiah-kha, chhiu2 koann7 e5, pou7-kiann5 khi3 Hu2-siann5.
Chong2-chek-a3 kiann5 kau3 poann3-lou7 e5 si5, bo5 se3-ji7 soa3 that tioh8 chioh8-thau5. I e5 kha-chng2-kah soa3 hiauh khi2-lai5, koh teh lau5-huih, sit8-chai7 chin thiann3. Chong2-si7 i chin hoann-hi2 kong2: “Ho2 kai-chai3 goa2 bo5 chheng7-e5, na7 beh u7 chheng7, kin-a2-jit8 goa2 e5 e5 i2-keng phainn2-khi3 lah.” Au7-lai5 i chiu7 jip8-khi3 Hu2-siann5 e5 chit8-keng gin5-hang5, kio3-cho3 Khoan3-giap8 gin5-hang5 (hian7-si5 e5 thou2-te7 gin5-hang5) e5 mng5-khau2 beh theng3-hau7 khui-mng5, in-ui7 hit-si5 iau2 chin cha2, Chong2-chek-a3 kin-a2-jit8 lai5 si7 beh nia2-chinn5.
Chong2-chek-a3 in-ui7 chin khiam7, sou2-i2 i e5 chheng7-chhah bo5 ho2, si7 bai2-bai2.
Cha2-si5 na7 u7 lang5 beh chhiann3 lang5 cho3-kang, tioh8 khi3 Khoan3-giap8 gin5-hang5 khau2, in-ui7 hia u7 chin che7 chhou-kang-lang5 teh theng3-hau7 hou7 lang5 chhiann3.
Hit-jit8 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 oa2-lai5 Chong2-chek-a3 hia, ka7 i kong2, “Iu2-e3-a2 li2 beh choan2-chiah8 bo5? Kin-a2-jit8 chin ho2 jit8, a-hiann khiam3 chin che7.” (kng si2-lang5--e5, Tai5-lam5 kio3-cho3 a-hiann) I3-su3 si7 khoann3 i si7 chit8 e5 chhou-kang-lang5, beh kio3 i khi3 kng si2-lang5.
Thai3 e7 an2-ni? In-ui7 i sui-bong2 ho2-giah8, iau2-ku2 ti7 i e5 goa7-mau7 bo5 chhin-chhiunn7 ho2-giah8 lang5.
Sio2 peng5-iu2 phou2-thong lang5 long2 si7 chin ai3 khoann3 lang5 e5 goa7-mau7.
Lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou ti7 se3-kan e5 si5 ma7 si7 bat hou7 lang5 khoann3-khin. Tng-si5 e5 lang5 kong2: “Chit e5 Ia5-sou kiam2 m7-si7 bak8-chhiunn7 mah?” “Kiam2 m7-si7 Iok-sek e5 kiann2 mah?” Koh hou7 Na2-tan3-giap8 ka7 Hui-lek8 kong2 “Na2-sat-lek8 e5 chhut sim2-mih8 ho2-mih8?” (Iok-han7 1:46)
Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 kim-ku3 ka7 lan2 kong2 “Siong7-te3 bo5 eng7 goa7-mau7 chhu2 lang5”. (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 10:34)
Na7 u7 si5-kan thang soat-beng5 Pi2-tek chainn2-iunn7 thoan5 to7-li2 hou7 goa7-pang lang5 Ko-ni5-liu5, chiu7-si7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 khoann3 cho3 bo5 chheng-khi3, be7 kham-tit cho3 Siong7-te3 e5 soan2-bin5--e5. A2-si7 beh lau5 ti7 hun-pan e5 si5 chiah kong2 iah8 ho2. (T. H. C.)
12 Geh8 20 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Boh8-tit kiann, in-ui7 goa2 po3 lin2 toa7 hoann-hi2 e5 ho2 siau-sit, hou7 peh-sinn3 long2 u7 hun7. (Lou7-ka 2:10)
Sio2 peng5-iu2 ti7 chia u7 2 hang7 siau-sit, chit8-hang7 si7 phainn2--e5, chit8-hang7 si7 ho2--e5, lan2 ai3 thiann to2 chit8-khoan2 ah? Chu7-jian5 ai3 thiann ho2--e5, hoann-hi2--e5, thang lai5 sann-kap hoann-hi2, kiam2 m7-si7 an2-ni? Chong2-si7 u7 si5 m7-na7 bo5 ho2--e5, tian-to3 si7 chin phainn2--e5, hou7 lang5 thiann liau2 chin kiann. Goa2 kong2 chit8 e5 hou7 lin2 thiann: Cha2 Siong7-te3 e5 peh-sinn3 kap pai3-put8-a2 e5 phainn2-lang5 Hui-li7-su lang5 sann-thai5, thai5-su Siong7-te3 e5 peh-sinn3, ka-ki7 siunn7 Siong7-te3 si7 chin u7 lat8, koh chin thiann3 in. Cha2 in kap tui3-tek8 sann-thai5, a2-si7 tu2-tioh8 khun3-lan5 e5 su7 na7 kiu5 Siong7-te3, Siong7-te3 chiu7 thiann, chiu7 hou7 in peng5-an, khah iann5. Chhin-chhiunn7 koe3 Iok-tan3-ho5, kng Iok-kui7 choe3 thau5-cheng5 seng kiann5, ho5-chui2 chiu7 ta hou7 in koe3, kap Ia5-li7-ko lang5 kau-chian3, Na2-sia2 kng Iok-kui7 tiam7-tiam7 ka7 i seh8, lian5 chioh8-chhiunn5 e5 toa7-siann5, m7-bian2 khap8--i i to ka-ki7 to2 loh8-khi3.
Tann kap Hui-li7-su lang5 kau-chian3, na2-sai2 kng Iok-kui7 lai5-khi3, tui3-tek8 chit8-e7 ma7 su, tek-khak to5-chau2 hou7 lan2 thai5 si2 liau2-liau2. Bo5 phah-sng3 tu2-tu2 tui3-hoan2. Pai3 Siong7-te3 e5 peh-sinn3 m7-chai ui7-tioh8 in e5 choe7, ui7-tioh8 in bo5 jiat8-sim, bo5 keng3-khian5 pai3 Siong7-te3, Siong7-te3 i2-keng li7-khui in, m7 khoann3-kou3 in lah, in long2 m7-chai. Iok-kui7 chit8-e7 kng khi3, soa3 hou7 tui3-tek8 chhiunn2-khi3. Peh-sinn3 toa7-pai7, in e5 chiong-kun hou7 lang5 thai5-si2. Po3 siau-sit e5 lang5 kin2 chau2 to3 lai5 po3, tong-si5 e5 che3-si-thau5, ia7-si7 sian-ti, koh si7 Su7-su7 e5 lau7 sian-sinn I2-li7, thiann chit8-e7 tui3 siann5-mng5-lau5 poah8-loh8-lai5, am7-kun2 chek-tng7 soa3 si2 khiau3-khiau3. I e5 sim-pu7 thiann chit8 e5 toa7-kiann soa3 liu5-san2, thong siann5 e5 lang5 chin kiann toa7 thi5-khau3, khau3 an2-choann2?
1. Khau3 chai-iann2 Siong7-te3 m7-tih8--in, li7-khui in khi3 lah. <BR>2. Iok-kui7 hou7 pai3-put8 e5 lang5 chhiunn2-khi3, chin-chiann3 si7 bo5 the2-bian7, hian2-beng5 Siong7-te3 bo5 khoann3-kou3 in lah. <BR>3. Tui3 chia khi2 tioh8 choe3 tui3-tek8 e5 lou5-chai5, hou7 lang5 koan2, choe3 khou2-kang oann7 lang5 phah, koh oann7 lang5 bo5 hoann-hi2 lah.
Chai chham2 lah, sou2-i2 tai7-ke khui-siann khau3, chit-ho7 siau-sit lin2 ai3 thiann bo5? Un2-tang3 m7 ai3, chin-chiann3 si7 chhi-chham2, kian3-siau3, thang kiann e5 siau-sit.
Tann lan2 cha2-khi2 tian-to3-hoan2, lan2 si7 beh lai5 kong2 chit8-hang7 m7 na7 chit8 kok e5 lang5 sou2 u7 hun7, hoann-hi2 e5 siau-sit. Si7 choan5 se3-kai3, bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5 tou u7 hun7, li2 u7 hun7, lau7-su ia7 u7 hun7. Ji5-chhiann2 chit e5 siau-sit m7 si7 chi2 u7 koan-he7 su iann5 e5 su7, si7 koan-he7 choan5-jin5-lui7 e5 si2, oah8, chin-chiann3 si7 bo5 pi2 hoann-hi2 e5 ho2 siau-sit. M7 si7 hit si5 e5 lang5 hoann-hi2, hian7-chai7 koh chiong-lai5, kau3 tak8 se3-tai7, tak8 sou2-chai7 e5 lang5 thiann-tioh8, tou beh chhiunn3-koa o-lo2 Siong7-te3, toa7-toa7 kam2-sia7 I e5 thiann3 e5 ho2 siau-sit. Tann chiau3 lin2 siunn7 chit e5 ho2 siau-sit si7 sim2-mih8? Chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 ti7 Seng3-tan3-cheh sou2 beh sang3 lan2 siang7 toa7 koh kui3-khi3 e5 le2-mih8. Hit tong-si5 e5 hoann-hi2 kap kheng3-chiok e5 jiat8-nau7 chin chiann3 m7 si7 sio2-khoa2. Tann theng3-hau7 hun-pan e5 si5 sian-sinn chiah lai5 kong2 hit e5.
1. Siong7-te3 sou2 hou7 lang5 choe3 toa7 e5 le2-mih8, hit e5 hoann-hi2 e5 siau-sit si7 sim2-mih8? <BR>2. Li2 u7 chiap-siu7 tioh8 a2 iau2-boe7? <BR>3. Tann lan2 tioh8 eng7 sim2-mih8 thai3-tou7 lai5 sann-kap kheng3-chiok, hoann-hi2 chiap-siu7 hit e5 ho2 e5 siau-sit chiah ho2? (L. J. S.)
12 Geh8 27 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Gi7-lang5 e5 ki5-to2, i e5 lek8-liong7 u7 toa7 kong-hau7. (Nga2-kok 5: 16)
Ti7 1600 ni5 cheng5 A-hui-li7-ka e5 sou2-chai7 chit8-ui7 keng3-khian5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3 choe3 Mou5-ni-ka, i u7 chit8 e5 hau7-senn kio3 choe3 Ou3-kou2-su7-teng, i se3-han3 e5 si5 lau7-pe7 chiu7 si2 khi3. Lau7-bu2 chit8-si3-lang5 chiu2 i, lau7-bu2 it-seng e5 ki5-to2 si7 ai3 kiann2 choe3 chit8 e5 ho2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, na7-si7 kiann2 khiok bo5 ai3 chiau3 lau7-bu2 e5 ki5-thai7, ai3 se3-kan khah koe3-thau5 ti7 to7-li2, au7-lai5 khi3 kau3 Lo5-ma2 liu5-hak8 e5 si5, oan5-choan5 li7-khui to7-li2 soa3 kiann5 ti7 ou-am3 e5 lou7. Chong2-si7 lau7-bu2 toa3 ti7 kou3-hiong me5-jit8 to ui7-tioh8 i e5 kiann2 piann3-mia7 e5 ki5-to2 ai3 i hoe2-kai2, lau7-bu2 mui2-jit8 to lau5 bak8-sai2 tui3 Chu2 kiu5, tioh8 hou7 i e5 kiann2 hoan2-hoe2, u7 chit8 pai2 u7 chiong kiann2 e5 su7 ka7 chit e5 sian-sinn kong2 e5 si5, sian-sinn an2-ni an-ui3 i kong2 “Chhiann2 li2 an-sim tng2-khi3, Siong7-te3 it-teng7 e7 pang-chan7 li2, chhin-chhiunn7 li2 chit-khoan2 piann3-mia7 e5 ki5-to2, li2 e5 kiann2 tek-khak boe7 biat8-bo5.”
Ko2-jian5 si7 lah, u7 chit8-jit8 Ou2-kou2-su-teng ti7 hoe-hng5 teh san3-pou7 khoann3 hoe e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 thiann-tioh8 chit8 e5 siann tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 ka7 i kong2 “Theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8, theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8”. I chhek tioh8 sim chiu7 jip8-khi3 thak8 chheh-pang5 theh8 chit8-pun2 ku2-ku2 bo5 teh thak8 e5 Seng3-keng hian-khui chit8-e7 khoann3 hit chat Seng3-keng chiu7-si7 Lo5-ma2 13 chiunn 13-14 chat. “Sou2 kiann5 tioh8 toan-chiann3, chhin-chhiunn7 ti7 jit8-si5, boh8-tit hounn3-sek sia5-im5, boh8-tit sann-chinn oan3-tou3. Tioh8 chheng Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, boh8-tit ui7-tioh8 jiok8-the2 tou5-bou5, ti3-kau3 than3 su-iok8.”
Chit e5 si5-chun7 Ou2-kou2-su-teng, leng5-hun5 chhenn2 khi2-lai5 siunn7 tioh8 lau7-bu2, siunn7 tioh8 Siong7-te3. Tng2-khi3 kou3-hiong chhoe7 lau7-bu2 jin7-choe7, ia7 kong2 chit e5 keng-koe3. Lau7-bu2 chin-chiann3 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 kiann2 thiann-tioh8 “theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8” hit e5 siann e5 si5 tu2-tu2 i e5 ma-ma ti7 chhu3-nih8 ui7-tioh8 i teh ki5-to2, au7-lai5 Ou2-kou2-su-teng chiu7 chiann5-choe3 kau3-hoe7 chin chhut-mia5 e5 lang5, lang5 ia7 chheng i choe3 Seng3 Ou2-kou2-su-teng, i u7 kong2 “goa2 bo5 ti3-kau3 biat8-bo5, oan5-choan5 si7 tui3 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 mi5-jit8 piann3-mia7 ki5-to2 e5 kong-lo5. Gi7-lang5 e5 ki5-to2, i e5 lek8-liong7 u7 toa7 kong-hau7. (I. L. Chhi5)
